and three small banks.
The Asian, Pacific and Latin American operations have been transferred to
other Philip Morris management divisions, leaving a core European business
with 1990 sales of SFr4.3bn.
To this has been added the Kraft General Foods operations in Scandinavia,
France and Germany.
